en_306786_0	A group of eminent videographers and photographers of the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation and the Lake House voluntarily offered their expertise and conducted a training workshop for Army personnel serving in all units in Kilinochchi during 3 - 5 September at Barathipuram Advanced Physical Training School in Kilinochchi.
en_306786_1	A total of 60 Other Ranks enthusiastically participated in the three-day long training workshop, following an initiative taken by the Commander, Security Forces - Kilinochchi, Major General Niyshshanka Ranawana.
en_306786_2	This basic course was instructed by Mr. Jayamimala Perera, Deputy Director (Camera Operator & Training), SLRC, Mr. Nihal Tissera, Deputy Director (Recording), SLRC, Mr Asoka Jayasekara Senior Cameraman, SLRC and Mr Thilak Perera, Photographer at Lake House.
